Docs.example:
Bad example:

public bool IsOdd (int x)
{
	// (x % 2) won't work for negative numbers (returns -1)
	return ((x % 2) == 1);
}

Good example:

public bool IsOdd (int x)
{
	return ((x % 2) != 0);
}

Good example (faster):

public bool IsOdd (int x)
{
	return ((x & 1) == 1);
}

